  "architecturePrompt": "Build an end-to-end Microsoft Fabric analytics platform. Ingest operational data from an on-prem SQL Server using a Fabric Data Pipeline and a Mirrored Database, and stream IoT telemetry through an Eventstream into an Eventhouse with a KQL Database for real-time analytics. Land raw data in OneLake, then use Fabric Notebooks and Dataflow Gen2 to process it through Bronze, Silver, and Gold Lakehouse layers, with a Warehouse for curated marts. Expose a Semantic Model in Direct Lake mode to a Power BI Report and a Real-Time Dashboard. Provision a Microsoft Fabric Capacity (F64) for the workload. Add a Fabric Data Agent for natural-language data Q&A."
